<L>You &s;peak it then&mdash;and do not mouth it, come,</L>
<L>Yet be not too tame neither&mdash;<HI>Shake&s;pear</HI>&mdash;Hum!</L>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lord Duberly.</SPEAKER>
<L>Rabbit it! be&s;t let the&s;e logs alone.</L>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lady Duberly</SPEAKER>
<L>What Epilogues&mdash;why they are all the ton.</L>
